{"type":"text","timestamp":1773482750280,"sessionID":"ses_314328d09ffeHamS8Go5GE0ezF","part":{"id":"prt_cebcf1b43001cQ33AqXDPAS3pg","sessionID":"ses_314328d09ffeHamS8Go5GE0ezF","messageID":"msg_cebcf123c001vaOJrbmVdmQaOB","type":"text","text":"### Step 3: Update launch.ts and resume.ts to use flushState() and onBeforeDestroy\n\nNow I need to update the onQuit and SIGINT handlers in both `launch.ts` and `resume.ts` to use `flushState()` instead of `saveState()`, and wire up the `onBeforeDestroy` callback.\n\nFirst, update the import in launch.ts:","time":{"start":1773482750280,"end":1773482750280}}}
